		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">marvelus10 wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">Today I went looking for some sort of grid pattern test for my SNES, I wanted to try and calibrate my TV with it.<br /><br />I found this, <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.nintendoplayer.com/unreleased/dsp-1/">http://www.nintendoplayer.com/unreleased/dsp-1/</a><!-- m --> unfortunitely it did not work with my SD2SNES all I got was a half blue screen.</div><br /><br />I talked to ikari_01 and he told me how to fix it.<br />Following bits need to be changed:<br /><br />0x7fd5 -&gt; 0x20<br />0x7fd6 -&gt; 0x03<br /><br /><a href="http://misc.mupfelofen.de/dsp1demo.zip" class="postlink">Download</a><br /><br />Works on any emulator now plus on real hardware via sd2snes.<br /><br />Greets<br />Michael

		

